Package: wavetask
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Plasma 6 task manager with macOS-style zoom
 WaveTask is a Plasma 6 task manager applet with macOS-style dock zoom
 animation, icon mirroring, and multiple visual skins. It integrates with
 KDE Activities and supports smart launcher badges and progress indicators.
